OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FThe number of children in care in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland is on the rise.
OL,9,FOver the past five years there's been
OL,10,Falmost a 25% rise and experts,
OL,11,Ffamilies and campaigners have all
OL,12,Fexpressed their dismay at what they
OL,13,Fsay is a system in crisis.
OL,15,FThere's no doubt that being a social
OL,16,Fworker in Northern Ireland is tough.
OL,17,FLike many other parts of the health
OL,18,Fand social care system, recruitment
OL,19,Fand staff retention is a massive issue.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/21
