OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FSocial workers also have to navigate
OL,7,Fthe most complex of situations, often
OL,8,Fparachuting in to difficult family
OL,9,Fdynamics, sometimes against the
OL,10,Fbackdrop of mental health issues or
OL,11,Fsubstance abuse and ensuring the best
OL,12,Foutcome for children can be
OL,13,Fchallenging.
OL,15,FThere has been a recognition of the
OL,16,Fneed for reform of the service for
OL,17,Fsome time.
