OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FOver two years ago, Professor Ray
OL,7,FJones, an expert in social care was
OL,8,Fengaged to conduct a review of
OL,9,Fchildren's services. The review cost
OL,10,Faround #2m.
OL,12,FFamilies, professionals and
OL,13,Fpoliticians were engaged.
OL,15,FThe review which was submitted over
OL,16,Ftwo years ago was 288 pages long, made
OL,17,F53 recommendations and provided a
OL,18,Fblueprint for how to fix an ailing
OL,19,Fsystem.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/21
