OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FProfessor Jones told UTV, that his
OL,7,Freview is gathering dust.
OL,9,FSince he completed his body of work,
OL,10,FProfessor Jones says he has made
OL,11,Fefforts to try and persuade
OL,12,Fpoliticians to get some of his
OL,13,Frecommendations into action.
OL,15,FAnd while both the Department of
OL,16,FHealth and the Department of Justice
OL,17,Fsay they accept most of his
OL,18,Frecommendations, he remains frustrated
OL,19,Fby what he sees as paralysis in
OL,20,FStormont.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/21
