OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FHe says that this is a body of work
OL,7,Fwhich should be made a priority not
OL,8,Fjust by the Department of Health but
OL,9,Fby the entire Northern Ireland
OL,10,FExecutive.
OL,12,FWhen I ask Professor Jones about what
OL,13,Fhis biggest concern is when looking at
OL,14,Fthe rising number of children being
OL,15,Fput into care, his answer is blunt.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/21
