OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FThe welfare of the children involved.
OL,7,FHe's worried not just about the act of
OL,8,Fremoving a child from the family but
OL,9,Fthe risks of placing them in an
OL,10,Finappropriate care setting which could
OL,11,Fput them at risk.
OL,13,FFreedom of Information reports show
OL,14,Fone trust has been sending kids as far
OL,15,Fas Scotland or the Republic of Ireland
OL,16,Fand spending hundreds of thousands of
OL,17,Fpounds on AirBNBs to accommodate
OL,18,Fchildren which Professor Jones says
OL,19,Fraises serious safeguarding issues but
OL,20,Fis an issue which he raised in the
OL,21,Fcourse of his review.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/21
