OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FSome families, from across NI, who are
OL,7,Finvolved with children and social
OL,8,Fservices are worried about the
OL,9,Fpressures the system is under and what
OL,10,Fthey see as the current lack of
OL,11,Faccountability within those social
OL,12,Fwork teams.
OL,14,FPrivacy concerns for children involved
OL,15,Fas well as the risk of identifying
OL,16,Fsocial workers has meant anyone that
OL,17,Fspoke to us on camera had to be
OL,18,Fanonymous, unnamed and we couldn't get
OL,19,Finto the specifics of their individual
OL,20,Fcases.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/21
