OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FLike most of these situations, there
OL,7,Fare complexities but there are also
OL,8,Fcommon themes from what these families
OL,9,Fand the several families that I spoke
OL,10,Fto off camera tell me about.
OL,12,FThey feel there's a power imbalance,
OL,13,Fthat the system is difficult to
OL,14,Fnavigate. They feel that if a
OL,15,Fsituation gets too complex that the
OL,16,Fdefault action is to take the kids
OL,17,Faway. They tell me the stigma of
OL,18,Fhaving social services involved means
OL,19,Fthat these issues are rarely spoken
OL,20,Fabout publicly.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/21
