OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FMany say that they have voluntarily
OL,7,Fand at their own expense completed
OL,8,Fparenting courses, self-development
OL,9,Fcourses in an effort to try to either
OL,10,Fget increased contact with their
OL,11,Fchildren or get them back.
OL,13,FThey all say that while they
OL,14,Facknowledge social workers have to
OL,15,Fconsider what is best for the kids,
OL,16,Fthere are also times when they feel
OL,17,Ffamilies could have received more help.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/21
