OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FFor instance there are cases of kids
OL,7,Fbeing taken on the ground of being 'at
OL,8,Frisk of emotional abuse' or 'at risk
OL,9,Fof neglect'.
OL,11,FMany of the families I spoke to argue,
OL,12,Frightly or wrongly, that perhaps a
OL,13,Ffamily who could get more support to
OL,14,Fovercome these challenges could be
OL,15,Fspared the trauma of separation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/21
