OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FMany of those who I spoke to tell of
OL,7,Fserious mental health effects of
OL,8,Flosing their children, both their own
OL,9,Fmental health and that of their kids,
OL,10,Fanother issue which Professor Jones is
OL,11,Fconcerned about.
OL,13,FThere is no easy fix for this system.
OL,14,FProfessor Jones believes an arms
OL,15,Flength body like a children's
OL,16,Fdirectorate to oversee all trusts
OL,17,Fwould be one way of regulating the
OL,18,Fsystem, using resources more
OL,19,Fefficiently and ensuring
OL,20,Faccountability.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/21
