OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FIn his words, he says that it needs
OL,7,Fsomeone who goes to bed thinking of
OL,8,Fthe reformation of the system and
OL,9,Fwakes up still consumed by this. As
OL,10,Fdetailed in the statement below, the
OL,11,FDepartment of Health says it is
OL,12,Fwilling to work on this idea but over
OL,13,Ftwo years after Professor Jones handed
OL,14,Fover his review, he's urging action.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/21
