OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,FA statement from the Department of
OL,7,FHealth said: "A Children's Social Care
OL,8,FServices Reform Programme was
OL,9,Festablished in April 2023 in order to
OL,10,Faddress the issues that led to the
OL,11,Freview by Professor Ray Jones, which
OL,12,Fwas subsequently published in June
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,F"The majority of the review's 53
OL,16,Frecommendations have already been
OL,17,Faccepted by the Health Minister and
OL,18,Fwork has commenced to implement them,
OL,19,Falthough many cannot be implemented in
OL,20,Ffull without greater investment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/21
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
