OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,F"The Programme is now moving to a new
OL,7,Fphase that will be underpinned by a
OL,8,Ffive-year strategic plan.
OL,10,F"This will provide a clear vision and
OL,11,Fa focus on a small number of strategic
OL,12,Fpriorities for the purpose of driving
OL,13,Fmeaningful and sustainable change
OL,14,Facross the system.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/21
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
