OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,F"The plan will prioritise supporting
OL,7,Ffamilies to enable them to stay safe,
OL,8,Fwell and together. Under the
OL,9,FProgramme, we have developed a new
OL,10,Fmodel of family support that would
OL,11,Foperate along a continuum of need and
OL,12,Finclude families referred to
OL,13,Fchildren's social care services.
OL,15,F"The aim would be to prevent children
OL,16,Fentering care or being able to return
OL,17,Fhome as quickly and safely as possible.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/21
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
