OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,F"The model would be implemented across
OL,7,FNI, but investment will be required to
OL,8,Fdo so. Seven of the review's 53
OL,9,Frecommendations are related to the
OL,10,Festablishment of a Children and
OL,11,FFamilies ALB (Arm's Length Body), for
OL,12,Fwhich the Minister has already
OL,13,Fpublicly indicated his support.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/21
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
