OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,F"The Justice Minister has also flagged
OL,7,Fher support for those recommendations.
OL,8,FBoth Ministers have agreed to work
OL,9,Ftogether to identify the steps
OL,10,Fnecessary to establish an ALB - a
OL,11,FRegional Children and Families
OL,12,FServices Authority, incorporating
OL,13,Fchildren's social care and youth
OL,14,Fjustice services.
OL,16,F"It is accepted that working in
OL,17,Fchildren's social care services
OL,18,Frequires fully staffed, well-motivated
OL,19,Fand well-managed teams of social
OL,20,Fworkers and other staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G18/21
