OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,F"The Department is engaged in an
OL,7,Fextensive programme of social work
OL,8,Fworkforce reform, including
OL,9,Fsignificant investment in additional
OL,10,Fsocial work training places as well as
OL,11,Finvestment in a range of actions to
OL,12,Fensure the workforce is supported.
OL,14,F"Regarding accommodation, under the
OL,15,FChildren (Northern Ireland) Order
OL,16,F1995, all Health & Social Care (HSC)
OL,17,FTrusts have a duty to safeguard and
OL,18,Fpromote the welfare of children in
OL,19,Ftheir care, and to provide
OL,20,Faccommodation for them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G19/21
