OL,3,C'A system in crisis': Inside NI's
OL,4,Csocial care system
OL,6,F"The growth in the population of
OL,7,Flooked-after children over the past 10
OL,8,Fyears and the complexity of need
OL,9,Fwithin that population is putting
OL,10,Fpressure on placements across all HSC
OL,11,FTrust areas.
OL,13,F"Within the Children's Social Care
OL,14,FServices Reform Programme, a specific
OL,15,Fworkstream is focused on ensuring that
OL,16,Fthere is sufficient accommodation
OL,17,Favailable to meet the needs of all
OL,18,Fchildren in care. Other departments
OL,19,Fand their respective agencies are also
OL,20,Fengaged in that work, given the
OL,21,Finterface with other services."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G20/21
